Ep 17: Lines In The Sand
 The women head to Puerto Rico, but a battle royale erupts when the ladies confront Lisa and Ken over dinner.

All the ladies, except Carlton, head off for a vacation in Puerto Rico. The relaxation doesn't last long after Yolanda and Brandi confront Lisa about the doubts they have regarding their friendships. A battle royale erupts over dinner, and Lisa and Ken leave the table, calling it a sabotage attack.
